    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a factory limited-slip differential. This example has undergone essential preventative maintenance, including rear subframe reinforcement and a VANOS bulletproofing kit, addressing common platform weak points. The chassis remains taut, utilizing a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension for exceptional lateral grip. Finished in Silver Grey Metallic, this M3 represents a balanced mechanical package for the serious driving enthusiast looking for visceral feedback and linear power delivery.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
